  "description": "<p>We are looking for full time driver (for 10 & 14 feet lorry). Ideal candidate is expected to drive materials across outlets in Singapore and to customer location.</p><ul><li>Required Skill(s): Class 3 Driving License. Class 4 driving license will be an added advantage.</li><li>Fork lift license will be an added advantage.</li><li>Candidate with reasonable english fluency (spoken english) will be considered.</li><li>Locals are preferred.</li><li>Candidate must possess at least Primary/Secondary School/\"O\" Level</li><li>At least 2 Year(s) of working experience as driver is preferred.</li><li>6 day a week, monday to Saturday; Timing 8.30am until finish.</li></ul>",
